text: CairoNamed for Cairo, Egypt, but pronounced differently is a city in Grady County, Georgia, United States. As of the 2020 census, the city had a population of 10,179. The city is the county seat of Grady County. ==References== ==Other websites== * * City of Cairo from georgia.gov Category:Cities in Georgia (U.S. state) Category:County seats in Georgia
title: Cairo, Georgia
